{"tid":573432,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"因為ONE PIECE比我妹串，霸氣盡失","createTime":"2018-02-26T12:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T18:05:24.000Z","uid":41602,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f44dcc4cfc7466aa0c6253eebebdf339ccafc245","tid":573432,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:47:40.000Z","msg":"話說今日我整理書櫃既漫畫<br />\n我將成套ONE PIECE 八十幾本好整齊咁排列<br />\n當我發覺竟然唔見左其中一本第84本！！<br />\n<br />\n我每次買一本漫畫番黎之後，睇完就比我妹睇，佢睇完就比番我<br />\n所以我要知道究竟係唔見左定買漏一本，最簡單既方法就係叫我妹上網睇下有無睇過84本839-838話既內容....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（我妹正係睇單行本，而我會上網追，所以問佢記憶較為標準）<br />\n<br />\n咁好啦...佢睇左其中幾話，就話無印象，咁即係我有一期買漏左.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我為左不失霸氣攞番個尾彩....串左佢一句：妳睇少成本內容都唔知，應該係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢串番我轉頭：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證明D內容唔重要，睇少成集都唔覺眼唔影響囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038c61cd177170c6160550f9ce2af0fb4e8cde62","tid":573432,"uid":28306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的，重作"},{"pid":"06812ab4e2790725b8668b47d2209126a4ddb00c","tid":573432,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"038c61cd177170c6160550f9ce2af0fb4e8cde62","tid":573432,"uid":28306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的，重作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:57:29.000Z","msg":"真人真事....唔係整電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請問信和四樓仲有無得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1d2f4819cebb8d5462bfca73cfa54c2ae5efae","tid":573432,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢動畫成日回憶，睇少一兩集都冇所謂啦"},{"pid":"facbaf2cd3975509feede96a15f9e3deef9be5af","tid":573432,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"諗咗五分鐘都諗唔到點駁呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519d8c3aad898b188fb1e0acba852336ec31adaa","tid":573432,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e1d2f4819cebb8d5462bfca73cfa54c2ae5efae","tid":573432,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢動畫成日回憶，睇少一兩集都冇所謂啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"唔睇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d07c644f3f89d6db5a8320072a07d2eb4f70996","tid":573432,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06812ab4e2790725b8668b47d2209126a4ddb00c","tid":573432,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"038c61cd177170c6160550f9ce2af0fb4e8cde62","tid":573432,"uid":28306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的，重作"},"cite